From: Cai Huoqing <caihuoqing@baidu.com>
Date: Tue, 31 Aug 2021 21:55:52 +0800
Subject: drm/imx: imx-tve: Make use of the helper function
 devm_platform_ioremap_resource()
Git-commit: 344c50dd4954e4592c0a17784a1b23b92796719f
Patch-mainline: v5.19-rc1
References: jsc#PED-1166 jsc#PED-1168 jsc#PED-1170 jsc#PED-1218 jsc#PED-1220 jsc#PED-1222 jsc#PED-1223 jsc#PED-1225

Use the devm_platform_ioremap_resource() helper instead of
calling platform_get_resource() and devm_ioremap_resource()
separately

Signed-off-by: Cai Huoqing <caihuoqing@baidu.com>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/20210831135553.4426-1-caihuoqing@baidu.com
Signed-off-by: Philipp Zabel <p.zabel@pengutronix.de>
Acked-by: Patrik Jakobsson <pjakobsson@suse.de>
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/imx/imx-tve.c | 4 +---
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 3 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/imx/imx-tve.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/imx/imx-tve.c
index bc8c3f802a15..2b1fdf2cbbce 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/imx/imx-tve.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/imx/imx-tve.c
@@ -526,7 +526,6 @@ static int imx_tve_probe(struct platform_device *pdev)
 	struct device_node *np = dev->of_node;
 	struct device_node *ddc_node;
 	struct imx_tve *tve;
-	struct resource *res;
 	void __iomem *base;
 	unsigned int val;
 	int irq;
@@ -568,8 +567,7 @@ static int imx_tve_probe(struct platform_device *pdev)
 		}
 	}
 
-	res = platform_get_resource(pdev, IORESOURCE_MEM, 0);
-	base = devm_ioremap_resource(dev, res);
+	base = devm_platform_ioremap_resource(pdev, 0);
 	if (IS_ERR(base))
 		return PTR_ERR(base);
 
